Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 45ms
Set Padding 16

Hide
Type "cd /tmp/luban-demo && clear"
Enter
Show

Type `# 对Agent说: "让鲁班看看我这个skill: github.com/LearnPrompt/ai-news-radar"`
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 400ms

Type "./demo.sh"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 10s

Type "# 验料·访行·过尺·慢刨·回炉 → github.com/LearnPrompt/luban-skill"
Sleep 4s
Enter
Sleep 1500ms
